#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Approved tasks will have a green tick and tasks awaiting approval will have "
"a blue square dot. ![Crowdin "
"Approval](../_static/images/translation_guide/crowdin_status.png \"Crowdin "
"Approval\")"
