"choices.png \"Surveys\")"
msgstr ""
"![Encuestas](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-matrix-multiple-"
"choices.png \"Encuestas\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Dynamic Matrix**"
msgstr "**Matriz dinámica**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Dynamic Matrix type is similar to a [Multiple-Choice "
"Matrix](https://surveyjs.io/survey-creator/documentation/end-user-"
"guide#multiple-choice-matrix), but respondents can add and remove matrix "
"rows."
msgstr ""
"El tipo de matriz dinámica es similar a una [matriz de opciones múltiples] "
"(https://surveyjs.io/survey-creator/documentation/end-user-guide#multiple-"
"choice-matrix), pero los encuestados pueden agregar y eliminar filas de la "
"matriz."

