"text.png \"Texto múltiple\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:63
msgid "Multiple Text"
msgstr "Texto múltiple"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Panel**"
msgstr "**Panel**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Panel type is a container for other questions and panels. Use this type "
"to group several questions or panels and control them all together."
msgstr ""
"El tipo Panel es un contenedor para otras preguntas y paneles. Utilice este "
"tipo para agrupar varias preguntas o paneles y controlarlos todos juntos."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Dynamic Panel**"
msgstr "**Panel dinámico**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Dynamic Panel type is a template panel that can contain multiple "
"questions. Respondents can add and remove panels based on the template."
msgstr ""
"El tipo Panel dinámico es un panel de plantilla que puede contener varias "
"preguntas. Los encuestados pueden agregar y eliminar paneles según la "
"plantilla."

