"panel.png \"Dynamic Panel\")"
msgstr ""
"![Panel dinámico](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-dynamic-"
"panel.png \"Panel dinámico\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:65
msgid "Dynamic Panel"
msgstr "Panel dinámico"

