#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "The host to use for sending email"
msgstr "El host que se utilizará para enviar correo electrónico"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_PORT"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_PORT"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "Port to use for the SMTP server defined in `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`"
msgstr "Puerto a utilizar para el servidor SMTP definido en `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "25"
msgstr "25"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_USE_TLS"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_USE_TLS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Whether to use a TLS (secure) connection when talking to the SMTP server. "
"This is used for explicit TLS connections, generally on port 587"
msgstr ""
"Si se debe utilizar una conexión TLS (segura) al hablar con el servidor "
"SMTP. Esto se utiliza para conexiones TLS explícitas, generalmente en el "
"puerto 587."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "True"
msgstr "Verdadero"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Username to use for the SMTP server defined in `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. If empty, "
"Django won’t attempt authentication."
msgstr ""
"Nombre de usuario que se utilizará para el servidor SMTP definido en "
"`SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. Si está vacío, Django no intentará la autenticación."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Password to use for the SMTP server defined in `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. This "
"setting is used in conjunction with `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER` when "
"authenticating to the SMTP server. If either of these settings is empty, "
"Django won’t attempt authentication."
msgstr ""
"Contraseña a utilizar para el servidor SMTP definido en `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. "
"Esta configuración se utiliza junto con `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER` al "
"autenticarse en el servidor SMTP. Si alguna de estas configuraciones está "
"vacía, Django no intentará la autenticación."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_ADMINS"
msgstr "CMS_ADMINS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A list of all the people who get code error notifications, in format `\"Name"
" <name@example.com>, Another Name <another@example.com>\"`"
msgstr ""
"Una lista de todas las personas que reciben notificaciones de error de "
"código, en formato `\"Nombre <nombre@ejemplo.com>, Otro nombre "
"<otro@ejemplo.com>\"`"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL"
msgstr "DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Default email address to use for various automated correspondence from the "
"site manager(s)"
msgstr ""
"Dirección de correo electrónico predeterminada que se utilizará para "
"diversas correspondencias automatizadas de los administradores del sitio"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY"
msgstr "RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Google Recaptcha Public Key. https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/ will "
"need a Google account for RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY and RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY "
"creation"
msgstr ""
"Clave pública de Google Recaptcha. https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/ "
"necesitará una cuenta de Google para la creación de RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY y "
"RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY"
msgstr "RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "Google Recaptcha Private Key"
msgstr "Clave privada de Google Recaptcha"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_NUM_OF_WORKERS"
msgstr "CMS_NUM_OF_TRABAJADORES"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Gunicorn number of workers. Recommended value should be `(2 x $num_cores) + "
"1 `. For example, if your server has `4 CPU Cores`, this value should be set"
" to `9`, which is the result of `(2 x 4) + 1 = 9`"
msgstr ""
"Número de trabajadores de Gunicorn. El valor recomendado debe ser `(2 x "
"$num_cores) + 1 `. Por ejemplo, si su servidor tiene \"4 núcleos de CPU\", "
"este valor debe establecerse en \"9\", que es el resultado de \"(2 x 4) + 1 "
"= 9\"."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"[Gunicorn Workers "
"details](https://docs.gunicorn.org/en/latest/design.html#how-many-workers)"
msgstr ""
"[Detalles de los trabajadores "
"Gunicorn](https://docs.gunicorn.org/en/latest/design.html#how-many-workers)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_STATIC_VOLUME"
msgstr "CMS_STATIC_VOLUME"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
