"Installing Requirements section below."
msgstr ""
"Si está familiarizado con git y Docker Compose, ejecute estos comandos para "
"iniciar el entorno de desarrollo de Climweb localmente; de ​​lo contrario, "
"comience desde la sección Requisitos de instalación a continuación."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:51
msgid "Installing requirements"
msgstr "Requisitos de instalación"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:53
msgid ""
"If you haven’t already installed docker and Docker Compose on your computer "
"you can do so by following the instructions on "
"[https://docs.docker.com/desktop](https://docs.docker.com/desktop) and "
"[https://docs.docker.com/compose/install](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install)"
msgstr ""
"Si aún no ha instalado Docker y Docker Compose en su computadora, puede "
"hacerlo siguiendo las instrucciones en "
"[https://docs.docker.com/desktop](https://docs.docker.com/desktop) y "
"[https://docs.docker.com/compose/install](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:58
msgid ""
"Docker version 19.03 is the minimum required to build Climweb. It is "
"strongly advised however that you install the latest version of Docker "
"available. Please check that your docker is up to date by running `docker "
"-v`."
msgstr ""
"La versión 19.03 de Docker es el mínimo requerido para construir Climweb. "
"Sin embargo, se recomienda encarecidamente que instale la última versión de "
"Docker disponible. Verifique que su ventana acoplable esté actualizada "
"ejecutando `docker -v`."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:62
msgid ""
"You will also need git installed which you can do by following the "
"instructions on [https://www.linode.com/docs/development/version-"
"control/how-to-install-git-on-linux-mac-and-"
"windows](https://www.linode.com/docs/development/version-control/how-to-"
"install-git-on-linux-mac-and-windows)."
msgstr ""
"También necesitará tener instalado git, lo cual puede hacer siguiendo las "
"instrucciones en [https://www.linode.com/docs/development/version-"
"control/how-to-install-git-on-linux-mac-and-"
"windows](https://www.linode.com/docs/development/version-control/how-to-"
"install-git-on-linux-mac-and-windows)."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:65
msgid ""
"Once you have finished installing all the required software you should be "
